This file contains major changes to tcp-calc

##########################

v-0.06
	Fixed:
	Identification of unary plus and minus.
	Validation check of the expression for calculation.

##########################

v-0.05
	Added:
	Support for real numbers in the calculator.
	Partial identification of unary plus and minus
	in the expression for calculation.

##########################

v-0.04
	Added:
	Partial validation check of the expression for calculation.

##########################

v-0.03_2
	Minor code changes in the user balance check
	and calculator.
	
##########################

v-0.03_1
	Added:
	User authentication.
	
##########################

v-0.03
	Added:
	Database with user accounts.
	Logging of calculational queries.
	
##########################

v-0.02
	Added:
	Finite state machine (FSM).
	Calculator for integers from
	
	(https://www.programmersought.com/article/6248269569/).
	
	Removed:
	Chat functions.
	
##########################

v-0.01
	Start of CHANGES file.
	
	The initial source code is a copy of files from the cpp-chat directory
	of the archive of sample programs
	
	(http://www.stolyarov.info/books/extra/progintro_e2_examples.tgz)
	
	to the books of A. V. Stolyarov "Programming: an introduction to the profession"
	(russian: Столяров А. В. Программирование: введение в профессию)
	
	(http://www.stolyarov.info/books/programming_intro/e2).

##########################

FORMAT:

This file contains a list, in reverse chronological order, of major
breakages or added features in tcp-calc.
